headline: Scotiabank Reaffirms Buy on Mosaic (MOS) Despite Sector Headwinds
summary: The Mosaic Company (NYSE:MOS) is one of the 20 undervalued momentum stocks that are taking off. While Scotiabank has become more cautious on fertilizer stocks overall, Mosaic Co. (MOS) continues to stand out as an exception. Analyst Ben Isaacson reiterated a Buy rating on the stock, raising the price target to $42 from $34 in May […]
